file.name: classes.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: structs
  version: 2.3.1
servers:
  - url: /
paths: {}
components:
  schemas:
    tstiop.MyClass1:
      type: object
      required:
        - int1
      properties:
        _class:
          type: string
        int1:
          type: integer
          format: int32
      discriminator:
        propertyName: _class
    tstiop.MyClass2:
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass1"
        - type: object
          required:
            - int2
          properties:
            int2:
              type: integer
              format: int32
    tstiop.MyClass2Bis:
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass1"
        - type: object
          required:
            - int2
          properties:
            int2:
              type: integer
              format: int32
    tstiop.MyClass3:
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass2"
        - type: object
          required:
            - int3
            - bool1
          properties:
            int3:
              type: integer
              format: int32
            bool1:
              type: boolean
            string1:
              type: string
            nextClass:
              oneOf:
                - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass1"
                - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass2"
                - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass2Bis"
                - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass3"
              discriminator:
                propertyName: _class
    tstiop.StructJpackFlags:
      type: object
      properties:
        opt:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        def:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          default: 1
        rep:
          type: array
          items:
            type: integer
            format: int32
        myClass:
          oneOf:
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass1"
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass2"
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass2Bis"
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass3"
          discriminator:
            propertyName: _class
    tstiop.MyStructB:
      type: object
      properties:
        a:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        b:
          type: array
          items:
            type: integer
            format: int32
    tstiop.MyUnionA:
      oneOf:
        - type: object
          required:
            - ua
          properties:
            ua:
              type: integer
              format: int32
        - type: object
          required:
            - ub
          properties:
            ub:
              type: integer
              format: int32
              minimum: -128
              maximum: 127
        - type: object
          required:
            - us
          properties:
            us:
              type: string
    tstiop.MyStructF:
      type: object
      properties:
        a:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        b:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            format: byte
        c:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyStructB"
        d:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyUnionA"
        e:
          type: array
          items:
            oneOf:
              - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass1"
              - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass2"
              - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass2Bis"
              - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass3"
            discriminator:
              propertyName: _class
        f:
          oneOf:
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass1"
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass2"
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass2Bis"
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop.MyClass3"
          discriminator:
            propertyName: _class
